command:
:: sccache currently uses the full compiler commandline as input to the
:: cache hash key, so create a symlink to the task dir and build from
:: the symlink dir to get consistent paths.
if exist z:\build rmdir z:\build

"c:\Program Files\Mercurial\hg.exe" robustcheckout --sharebase y:\hg-shared --purge --upstream https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-unified --revision ec3dd3ee2ae4b3a63529a912816a110e925eb2d0 https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central .\build\src
